<collectingCountry id="F31CBCD0FF95BD43FE13FE1B88C1FD95" box="[399,451,491,512]" name="Laos" pageId="2" pageNumber="1551">Laos</collectingCountry>
. The currently known distribution is illustrated in 
<figureCitation id="1330E0C5FF95BD43FC5CFE1B8D01FD95" box="[960,1027,490,512]" captionStart="Map 1" captionStartId="1.[178,223,1480,1500]" captionTargetBox="[178,1085,714,1470]" captionTargetId="figure-204@1.[178,1085,714,1470]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="Map 1: Distributions of Neosclerus macer nov.sp. (open circle) and N. barbatulus ASSING (filled and open circles) in South Asia." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5302502" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5302502/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="1551">Map 1</figureCitation>
